 608    {

 618                // Use the seed to initialize a deterministic random number generator

 0620                using var sha256 = System.Security.Cryptography.SHA256.Create();
 0621                byte[] seedHash = sha256.ComputeHash(seedBytes);
 622

 0626                random.NextBytes(result);
 627            }
 628            else
 629            {
 630                // Use efficient batch generation from enclave
 0631                result = _enclaveWrapper.GenerateRandomBytes(length);
 632            }

 636        }
